1
00:00:14,320 --> 00:00:14,960
Chen Hui

2
00:00:15,640 --> 00:00:17,079
Why don't you just kill me?

3
00:00:17,519 --> 00:00:19,160
Killing you would be too easy.

4
00:00:19,160 --> 00:00:20,000
No fun in that.

5
00:00:20,879 --> 00:00:21,879
Let's play a bigger game.

6
00:00:22,199 --> 00:00:23,239
Where's He Siqi?

7
00:00:23,719 --> 00:00:25,320
Where did you hide He Siqi?

8
00:00:25,719 --> 00:00:26,559
Chu Feng and Qin Mo,

9
00:00:26,559 --> 00:00:28,039
when are they coming to save you?

10
00:00:28,280 --> 00:00:29,480
You really aren't afraid to die.

11
00:00:30,079 --> 00:00:31,399
Daring to challenge the police.

12
00:00:31,719 --> 00:00:33,240
Everyone has their own story.

13
00:00:34,560 --> 00:00:36,159
Now I'm a wanted man because of them.

14
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:39,039
Shouldn't I thank you properly?

15
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:48,799
Chen Hui

16
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:50,960
took revenge on Yu Tianfang

17
00:00:51,280 --> 00:00:52,240
and He Siqi.

18
00:00:52,799 --> 00:00:53,759
One is critically injured,

19
00:00:53,920 --> 00:00:54,960
the other is held hostage.

20
00:00:55,640 --> 00:00:56,439
The higher-ups

21
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:58,560
are taking this case very seriously.

22
00:00:58,920 --> 00:00:59,640
They've ordered

23
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:01,320
that all cases related to Chen Hui

24
00:01:01,320 --> 00:01:02,320
be merged,

25
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:03,560
and the task force

26
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:05,000
must marshal all resources

27
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:06,760
to bring him to justice.

28
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:24,359
Hello, who is this?

29
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:27,319
Is Qin Weicheng your father?

30
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:28,400
Who are you?

31
00:01:29,079 --> 00:01:31,319
He was the first to push me to the brink.

32
00:01:31,599 --> 00:01:32,439
He was truly impressive.

33
00:01:33,079 --> 00:01:34,200
You young ones

34
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:35,560
are nothing compared to him.

35
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:36,799
Where's Yu Tianfang?

36
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,079
Put Chu Feng on the phone.

37
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:43,120
There's no telling

38
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,359
what trick Chen Hui will pull next.

39
00:01:44,879 --> 00:01:46,719
Everyone, prepare contingency plans.

40
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:48,480
Be ready for anything.

41
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,079
Yes, sir!

42
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,319
Reporting in.

43
00:01:51,319 --> 00:01:51,920
Qin Mo,

44
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,159
you can't be part of Chen Hui's case.

45
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:54,439
Chief, Captain Chu,

46
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:55,719
it's a call from Chen Hui.

47
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:10,120
I've got Yu Tianfang.

48
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,479
If you don't want him dead,

49
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:12,879
come see me tomorrow.

50
00:02:13,199 --> 00:02:15,159
Only Chu Feng and Qin Mo can come.

51
00:02:15,159 --> 00:02:17,680
If I see a third person,

52
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:20,080
then he's a dead man.

53
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:20,680
Chen Hui,

54
00:02:21,159 --> 00:02:23,120
I need proof Yu Tianfang is alive first.

55
00:02:23,319 --> 00:02:24,199
Sure.

56
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,800
Don't listen to him!

57
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:29,039
He's set a trap here!

58
00:02:29,199 --> 00:02:30,280
Forget about me!

59
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,039
You heard him, right?

60
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,599
Whether Yu Tianfang lives or not,

61
00:02:35,599 --> 00:02:36,439
that's up to you.

62
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:37,840
You bastard!

63
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:44,159
You're a dead man!

64
00:02:44,439 --> 00:02:44,879
I...

65
00:02:48,439 --> 00:02:48,800
Chief.

66
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:49,599
Captain.

67
00:02:49,879 --> 00:02:50,719
What do we do?

68
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,560
By the recusal rule,

69
00:02:52,759 --> 00:02:53,840
I can't be involved in this case.

70
00:02:54,639 --> 00:02:55,960
But Chen Hui specifically demanded me.

71
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,080
If I don't go,

72
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:58,400
the hostage will likely be in danger.

73
00:02:59,000 --> 00:02:59,479
Chief,

74
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,919
Chen Hui clearly wants revenge on us both.

75
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,120
I'll just lead the team in.

76
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,080
Chief,

77
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,879
saving the hostage comes first.

78
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,800
I promise I won't break protocol.

79
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:09,840
I'll just assist from the side,

80
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,400
and follow all your orders.

81
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:27,319
Boss.

82
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,800
Please give me a sip of water.

83
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,719
Haven't you always wanted me dead?

84
00:03:34,639 --> 00:03:36,879
Now you're begging your enemy for water?

85
00:03:37,879 --> 00:03:39,840
You've got no backbone at all.

86
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:41,599
I don't want to die.

87
00:03:41,599 --> 00:03:42,439
Then how about this:

88
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,080
bark like a dog a couple times,

89
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:46,319
and I'll give you water.

90
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:53,520
Just like a mangy cur.

91
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:54,800
I am a mangy cur.

92
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,000
Boss, please,

93
00:03:56,759 --> 00:03:57,479
just one sip.

94
00:04:08,319 --> 00:04:09,479
I'm really curious

95
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,479
how you ended up

96
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,479
where you are today.

97
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,120
For money, of course.

98
00:04:15,639 --> 00:04:17,720
I didn't want to be poor my whole life.

99
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:20,120
You probably won't believe this,

100
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,680
but back then, my grades,

101
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:23,079
when I was in school,

102
00:04:23,079 --> 00:04:25,040
were the best in the whole school.

103
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,920
I could've easily got into a top college.

104
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,160
Then how did you end up

105
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,839
going down this crooked path?

106
00:04:32,199 --> 00:04:33,079
Couldn't help it.

107
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,600
Smart guys

108
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:37,279
are always popular with girls.

109
00:04:37,519 --> 00:04:39,360
One girl kept chasing after me.

110
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,680
I couldn't resist,

111
00:04:41,439 --> 00:04:42,560
and she got pregnant.

112
00:04:42,759 --> 00:04:44,439
She had the kid and ran off.

113
00:04:44,439 --> 00:04:46,040
I got expelled from school.

114
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,079
Now that I think about it,

115
00:04:49,519 --> 00:04:52,120
that girl looked a lot like He Siqi.

116
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,199
Every time He Siqi and I

117
00:04:53,199 --> 00:04:54,680
slept together,

118
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:57,079
all I could think about was her.

119
00:04:58,279 --> 00:04:59,480
You old creep.

120
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:01,079
You bastard.

121
00:05:01,279 --> 00:05:02,399
I'll show you.

122
00:05:02,959 --> 00:05:04,519
You still want to fight me?

123
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:06,560
Over here.

124
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:12,079
Doctor,

125
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:13,199
how is she?

126
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,800
We have to wait for the hematoma to absorb.

127
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:15,800
She can't get too emotional.

128
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:17,800
A ruptured capsule is very dangerous.

129
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,120
In those years,

130
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:24,680
I had to raise my kid.

131
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,319
I worked odd jobs everywhere.

132
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:28,600
It was too exhausting, I couldn't take it.

133
00:05:29,079 --> 00:05:31,120
So I followed a boss into the underworld.

134
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,399
I was good at math,

135
00:05:32,399 --> 00:05:34,439
so the boss had me manage all his books.

136
00:05:34,439 --> 00:05:35,279
And me?

137
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:37,160
I transferred all the money in his account

138
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:39,079
into my own.

139
00:05:39,079 --> 00:05:41,959
That's how my loan-shark business began.

140
00:05:42,759 --> 00:05:44,160
Weren't you afraid your boss

141
00:05:44,759 --> 00:05:46,040
would come after you?

142
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,759
Let me tell you,

143
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:48,759
this boss,

144
00:05:49,079 --> 00:05:50,759
I had evidence on him.

145
00:05:50,759 --> 00:05:52,399
I reported him anonymously.

146
00:05:52,399 --> 00:05:53,360
He'd killed people.

147
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:55,079
He got the death sentence.

148
00:05:55,079 --> 00:05:56,360
How could he ever find me?

149
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:57,800
Chen Hui,

150
00:05:58,319 --> 00:05:59,639
you really are a monster.

151
00:05:59,639 --> 00:06:00,920
Rot in hell!

152
00:06:02,279 --> 00:06:03,639
I don't care.

153
00:06:04,279 --> 00:06:05,360
Even if I die, I'm dragging

154
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:07,639
Chu Feng and Qin Mo down with me.

155
00:06:07,839 --> 00:06:10,800
We'll all go to hell together.

156
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,279
On the road to the afterlife,

157
00:06:12,279 --> 00:06:15,000
once you drink Meng Po's soup,

158
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,920
you'll forget He Siqi forever.

159
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:17,839
Don't touch them.

160
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,279
If you've got the guts, come after me.

161
00:06:19,279 --> 00:06:19,920
Come at me!

162
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,279
I am coming after you.

163
00:06:21,759 --> 00:06:23,480
You have no idea.

164
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:25,040
I'll make you understand

165
00:06:25,879 --> 00:06:27,920
what it feels like to experience

166
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:30,519
pain and pleasure together.

167
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:53,839
Don't move.

168
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,079
You absolutely cannot get out of bed.

169
00:06:59,279 --> 00:07:00,240
The hematoma on your spleen

170
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,600
is swollen like a blood sac.

171
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,199
It could burst at any moment.

172
00:07:03,199 --> 00:07:04,319
Whatever you do, don't get up.

173
00:07:04,879 --> 00:07:05,680
Tianfang,

174
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,040
where's my husband?

175
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:07,720
I don't know.

176
00:07:09,319 --> 00:07:11,519
Captain Chu and Officer Qin made it clear

177
00:07:11,519 --> 00:07:12,800
you should focus on recovering.

178
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:13,800
Everything else,

179
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:14,839
the police will handle.

180
00:07:15,519 --> 00:07:16,040
Got it.

181
00:07:28,639 --> 00:07:29,279
What are you doing?

182
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,120
I really hope

183
00:07:31,519 --> 00:07:33,360
Chu Feng and Qin Mo hurry up.

184
00:07:34,079 --> 00:07:35,439
One pull of the trigger,

185
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,680
and you can go up in smoke

186
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,920
together with them.

187
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,360
Before they even arrive,

188
00:07:43,199 --> 00:07:44,839
you'll die of gas poisoning first.

189
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:45,600
Idiot.

190
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,720
I'm not going to stick around here.

191
00:07:47,879 --> 00:07:49,360
Enjoy it all by yourself.

192
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:51,519
Goodbye.

193
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:30,120
Why hasn't he called yet?

194
00:08:30,399 --> 00:08:30,959
Don't panic.

195
00:08:31,399 --> 00:08:32,360
The more critical the moment,

196
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:33,600
the steadier we have to be.

197
00:08:33,879 --> 00:08:35,000
We have our tech team backing us up,

198
00:08:35,639 --> 00:08:36,120
and besides,

199
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:38,000
SWAT is on their way to assist.

200
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:41,519
I hope Yu Tianfang is okay.

201
00:08:53,639 --> 00:08:54,080
Hello?

202
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,639
Chu Feng and I are ready.

203
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,399
My favorite thing is breaking up couples.

204
00:08:57,759 --> 00:08:59,279
I want you two to split up.

205
00:09:00,559 --> 00:09:01,080
Chu Feng.

206
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:03,720
Don't you want to avenge your master?

207
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,720
Then go

208
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:07,000
to the river where I killed Qin Weicheng.

209
00:09:07,759 --> 00:09:09,240
I left a clue there.

210
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:12,480
You asshole!

211
00:09:12,759 --> 00:09:13,759
Don't get worked up.

212
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,279
If you want to avenge your father,

213
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:17,639
go to the diner where you almost got me.

214
00:09:17,799 --> 00:09:19,399
See if your luck holds out.

215
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:22,240
See if you can find the other clue I left.

216
00:09:22,919 --> 00:09:24,840
Remember, both clues must be combined

217
00:09:25,519 --> 00:09:26,440
to find me.

218
00:09:26,639 --> 00:09:28,159
What kind of game are you playing?

219
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,279
If you don't find the clues,

220
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:31,879
Yu Tianfang dies.

221
00:09:31,879 --> 00:09:33,360
You only have ten minutes.

222
00:09:35,879 --> 00:09:36,759
Ten minutes.

223
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:38,759
Hello?

224
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,240
He's definitely toying with us on purpose.

225
00:09:48,759 --> 00:09:50,080
But right now, we have no choice.

226
00:09:50,679 --> 00:09:51,639
For the hostage's safety,

227
00:09:51,639 --> 00:09:52,440
we have to play along.

228
00:09:52,759 --> 00:09:53,440
I'll go to the riverside.

229
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,159
You go to the restaurant.

230
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,279
Let's go, Captain Chu.

231
00:09:55,879 --> 00:09:56,759
How about I go to the riverside,

232
00:09:56,759 --> 00:09:57,679
and you guys go to the resort.

233
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:58,679
The surveillance equipment can pinpoint

234
00:09:58,679 --> 00:10:00,039
the rough location of Chen Hui's call.

235
00:10:00,159 --> 00:10:01,519
He's not at either of those two places.

236
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:04,759
There's no time, Master.

237
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:06,840
We told traffic police to fully cooperate.

238
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:07,960
Green lights all the way.

239
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:08,799
They'll help you get there.

240
00:10:09,159 --> 00:10:09,559
Master.

241
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:10,519
Go.

242
00:10:11,639 --> 00:10:12,080
Got it.

243
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:15,120
Wait for backup. Don't act rashly.

244
00:10:16,559 --> 00:10:17,559
I guarantee I'll complete the mission.

245
00:10:43,639 --> 00:10:44,559
The door isn't even locked?

246
00:10:45,159 --> 00:10:46,519
You really underestimate yours truly.

247
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:49,720
I'll teach you not to underestimate me.

248
00:10:50,279 --> 00:10:51,600
If yours truly catches you,

249
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,960
I'll break your damn legs.

250
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,600
I'll skin you alive.

251
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:57,320
You old son of a bitch!

252
00:11:00,879 --> 00:11:01,759
There's still time,

253
00:11:01,759 --> 00:11:03,879
so I'll have some fun with you, little punk.

254
00:11:17,759 --> 00:11:19,159
Chen Hui is definitely playing us.

255
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,360
He said there are clues.

256
00:11:21,919 --> 00:11:22,720
Keep searching.

257
00:11:25,159 --> 00:11:25,879
Be careful!

258
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:04,840
Move!

259
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:08,840
Over here.
